@test no-error @@

Test that local variables shadow global variables:

@assert_eq[hello,AAAA,CCCC]
 @define[a][] AAAA @@
 @define[c][] CCCC @@
 @define[foo][a b] @a,@b,@c @@
 @foo[hello][@a]

Test that the body of a function is executed in the scope where it is defined,
not the scope of the caller.

@assert_eq[hello,AAAA,CCCC]
 @define[a][] AAAA @@
 @define[c][] CCCC @@
 @define[foo][a b] @a,@b,@c @@
 @define[c][] DDDD @@
 @foo[hello][@a]

End of tests.
